5. Add "What you'll get" preview
6. Update type definitions

### Sprint 3 (P1 - Social Proof)
7. Add SocialProofBanner to ConversionStep
8. Add InsightExpiryWarning (Loss Aversion)
9. Enhance FortunePreview with blur reveal

### Sprint 4 (Polish)
10. Mobile responsive testing
11. Animation timing refinement
12. Accessibility audit (reduced motion support)

---

## Dependencies

- No new npm packages required
- Uses existing CSS animation patterns from globals.css
- Uses existing Tailwind config patterns
